  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The plot is set as an investigation of extraterrestrial life in the future.  A detector on a certain planet sent back a life response and received a distress message, and then lost contact.  So the player will play a team of investigators and go to the target planet to investigate the situation.  During the investigation During the process, you accidentally entered the territory of an unknown civilization and were attacked by strange creatures.  Please try your best to survive and wait for rescue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will play the game with the first person.There will be a mission prompt in the map, arrive at the designated place to complete the mission, and complete all the tasks to clear the level </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be a lot of enemies along the way, shoot them with weapons to ensure your own safety </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be some special monsters among the enemies, which are very threatening, so kill them first</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Material</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Model:Unreal Marketplace/ Cgtrader/ Artstation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character animation:Unreal Marketplace/ Mixamo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Image:Unreal Marketplace/ Deviantart</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest of the materials are all from the Unreal Marketplace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The plot is set as an investigation of extraterrestrial life in the future.  A detector on a certain planet sent back a life response and received a distress message, and then lost contact.  So the player will play a team of investigators and go to the target planet to investigate the situation.  During the investigation During the process, you accidentally entered the territory of an unknown civilization and were attacked by strange creatures.  Please try your best to survive and wait for rescue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will play the game with the first person.There will be a mission prompt in the map, arrive at the designated place to complete the mission, and complete all the tasks to clear the level </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be a lot of enemies along the way, shoot them with weapons to ensure your own safety </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be some special monsters among the enemies, which are very threatening, so kill them first</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Material</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Model:Unreal Marketplace/ Cgtrader/ Artstation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character animation:Unreal Marketplace/ Mixamo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Image:Unreal Marketplace/ Deviantart</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest of the materials are all from the Unreal Marketplace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
